name: Exceeds Skull Archfiend
desc:
2 Level 6 monsters
This card's name becomes "Summoned Skull" while on the field, but it is still treated as an "Archfiend" card. If a "Summoned Skull" you control would be destroyed by battle or card effect, you can detach 1 material from this card instead. If this Xyz Summoned card you control is sent to your GY by your opponent's card: You can Special Summon 1 "Summoned Skull" from your hand, Deck, or GY.
